        "Description": "When a luxury cruise listed into the freezing Atlantic, there had been one life raft left and two women reaching for it. \r\rIsabella Caruso didn’t hesitate. She shoved an unnamed stranger back into the churning black water, ignored the desperate fingers clawing at the rubber, and safely assumed the woman was swallowed by the sea. \r\rThat was 20 years ago.\r\rNow, a new ICA contract has been signed by a woman who didn&apos;t drown, but endured.",
